---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import smilingImage from '../assets/images/Smiling about AI.png';
---

<Layout title="About - ex10x" description="Learn more about Chris Fossenier and the ex10x mission.">
	<section class="py-20">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">About</h1>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
				<div class="md:col-span-1">
					<div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden sticky top-24">
						<Image
							src={smilingImage}
							alt="Chris Fossenier smiling"
							width={400}
							height={400}
							class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-square"
							loading="eager"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="md:col-span-2 prose prose-gray max-w-none">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Hi, I'm Chris Fossenier</h2>

					<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
						I'm passionate about the intersection of AI and productivity. For years, I've been exploring how modern AI tools can help people work smarter, not harder—and I'm excited to share what I've learned.
					</p>

					<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
						The name "ex10x" represents my belief that with the right tools and techniques, anyone can dramatically amplify their output. Whether you're a developer, entrepreneur, or creative professional, AI can be your force multiplier.
					</p>

					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">What I Focus On</h3>

					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							<span><strong class="text-gray-900">Vibe Coding</strong> — Using AI assistants to write code faster and with less friction</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							<span><strong class="text-gray-900">Workflow Automation</strong> — Building systems that handle repetitive tasks automatically</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							<span><strong class="text-gray-900">Practical AI Applications</strong> — Real-world use cases that deliver immediate value</span>
						</li>
					</ul>

					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">My Approach</h3>

					<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
						I believe in learning by doing. Every technique I teach is something I use daily. I'm not interested in theoretical possibilities—I focus on what works right now, today.
					</p>

					<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
						Through my blog, videos, and personal sessions, I aim to give you actionable knowledge you can apply immediately. No fluff, no hype—just practical skills that make a real difference.
					</p>

					<div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Want to work together?</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
							I offer personal sessions for individuals and teams who want hands-on guidance tailored to their specific needs.
						</p>
						<a
							href="/book"
							class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-gray-900 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors"
						>
							Book a Session
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
